						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Celius wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Is it possible to keep track of the Program Counter?</div>
<br />When you execute a JSR command the PC is stored on the stack. You could JSR to a routine that will pull that and use as you want. AFAIK, the only way to read the PC is getting it from the stack.</div>

